These classes are fluid and are subject to change (adding or removal) 

Admin: 
functions - close accounts, encrypt data, send notifications, create new users

user:
ChangePassword -> change the password of the current user
ChangeEmail -> change the email of the current user
RecoverPassword -> recover password when lost. 

subs:
SubscriptionHandler -> subscribe/unsubscribe to services

payment:
PaymentHandler -> take input for payment options for subscription services

registration:
require usernames unique
require passwords to be adherent to recognized standards
require isp input

metrics:
query active accounts
measure rating of application

ispdata:
use service provider api to pull users relevant channels



